{
      "info": {
            "_postman_id": "ocr-api-collection",
            "name": "OCR + OpenAI IMEI Extraction API",
            "description": "API for extracting IMEI numbers from images using Tesseract OCR and OpenAI",
            "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
      },
      "item": [
            {
                  "name": "Extract IMEI from Image",
                  "request": {
                        "method": "POST",
                        "header": [],
                        "body": {
                              "mode": "formdata",
                              "formdata": [
                                    {
                                          "key": "image",
                                          "type": "file",
                                          "src": "/path/to/your/image.jpg",
                                          "description": "Image file containing IMEI text (JPEG, PNG, WebP, AVIF)"
                                    }
                              ]
                        },
                        "url": {
                              "raw": "http://localhost:5000/api/ocr/extract-imei",
                              "protocol": "http",
                              "host": ["localhost"],
                              "port": "5000",
                              "path": ["api", "ocr", "extract-imei"]
                        },
                        "description": "Upload an image and extract IMEI numbers from it\n\n**Request:**\n- Method: POST\n- Body: form-data with 'image' file field\n\n**Response:**\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"message\": \"IMEI extraction completed successfully\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"rawText\": \"Extracted text from image...\",\n    \"imeiNumbers\": [\"123456789012345\", \"987654321098765\"],\n    \"confidence\": \"high\",\n    \"processingTime\": 2500\n  }\n}\n```"
                  }
            },
            {
                  "name": "Extract NID from Images",
                  "request": {
                        "method": "POST",
                        "header": [],
                        "body": {
                              "mode": "formdata",
                              "formdata": [
                                    {
                                          "key": "nid_front",
                                          "type": "file",
                                          "src": "/path/to/your/nid_front.jpg",
                                          "description": "NID front image (required if nid_back not provided)"
                                    },
                                    {
                                          "key": "nid_back",
                                          "type": "file",
                                          "src": "/path/to/your/nid_back.jpg",
                                          "description": "NID back image (optional)"
                                    }
                              ]
                        },
                        "url": {
                              "raw": "http://localhost:5000/api/v1/ocr/extract-nid",
                              "protocol": "http",
                              "host": ["localhost"],
                              "port": "5000",
                              "path": ["api", "v1", "ocr", "extract-nid"]
                        },
                        "description": "Upload NID front and optional back images to extract the NID number\n\n**Request:**\n- Method: POST\n- Body: form-data with 'nid_front' (file) and optional 'nid_back' (file)\n\n**Response:**\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"message\": \"NID extracted successfully\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"nidNumber\": \"1234567890123\",\n    \"isValid\": true,\n    \"message\": \"NID number extracted successfully\",\n    \"processingTime\": 842\n  }\n}\n```"
                  }
            }
      ]
}
